Block B appears to be placed on top of Block A, though it is technically part of a single structure.

These blocks seem to interlock and form a single inseparable piece rather than being stacked separately.  However, adhering to the requested format, I'll present a step-by-step instruction. The best way to describe this "assembly" would be a simultaneous joining.
